Package: component-registry
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: RDK Component Registry (CR)
 The Component Registry is a central component in the RDK software stack
 that manages component registration and provides component lookup services.
 It uses RBUS for inter-component communication.
